      qemu: avoid dereferencing a NULL pointer (Alex Jia),
      qemu: Avoid loop of fake reboots (Jiri Denemark),
      qemu: Fix shutdown regression with buggy qemu (Jiri Denemark),
      remote: fix crash on OOM (Eric Blake)

