0.8.8: Feb 17 2011:
   - Features:
      sysinfo: expose new API (Eric Blake),
      cgroup blkio weight support. (Gui Jianfeng),
      smartcard device support (Eric Blake),
      qemu: Support per-device boot ordering (Jiri Denemark)

   - Documentation:
      docs: fix typos (Eric Blake),
