      Make sure virtTestCaptureProgramOutput has a body on Windows (Matthias Bolte),
      Fix export of virConnectAuthPtrDefault for MinGW builds (Matthias Bolte),
      Make sure uid_t and gid_t are available (Matthias Bolte)

